<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Your apartment listing is on its way — RentPal</title>
<style>
  body{margin:0;padding:0;background:#f0f2f5;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;}
  .wrap{max-width:560px;margin:32px auto;padding:0 12px 40px;}
  .header{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#141927 0%,#0C447C 100%);padding:24px 32px;border-radius:12px 12px 0 0;text-align:center;}
  .logo{font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#4A8FD4;letter-spacing:-0.5px;}
  .body{background:#fff;padding:36px 32px;border:1px solid #e4e7ed;border-top:none;border-radius:0 0 12px 12px;}
  h1{font-size:21px;font-weight:700;color:#0f1117;line-height:1.3;margin:0 0 16px;text-align:center;}
  p{font-size:14px;color:#5a6072;line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 16px;font-weight:300;}
  .divider{border:none;border-top:1px solid #f0f2f5;margin:24px 0;}
  .section-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.2px;color:#9299a8;margin-bottom:10px;}
  .step-row{display:flex;gap:11px;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:10px;}
  .dot{width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:#4A8FD4;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:8px;}
  .step-text{font-size:14px;color:#5a6072;line-height:1.75;font-weight:300;}
  strong{color:#0f1117;font-weight:500;}
  .reward-box{background:#f8f9fc;border-left:3px solid #4A8FD4;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:14px 16px;margin:20px 0;}
  .reward-box p{margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#5a6072;}
  .cta-wrap{text-align:center;margin:20px 0 4px;}
  .cta-btn{display:inline-block;background:#4A8FD4;color:#fff;padding:13px 28px;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;}
  .tg-wrap{text-align:center;margin-top:16px;}
  .tg-btn{display:inline-block;background:#0088cc;color:#fff;padding:13px 28px;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;}
  .footer{font-size:11px;color:#b0b6c3;line-height:1.7;margin-top:24px;text-align:center;}
  .footer a{color:#b0b6c3;}
  @media(max-width:600px){.wrap{padding:0 0 24px;margin:0 auto;}.header,.body{border-radius:0;border-left:none;border-right:none;}.header{padding:20px 20px;}.body{padding:28px 20px;}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo">rentpal</div>
  </div>
  <div class="body">

    <h1>Thanks for listing your place, {{firstName}}.</h1>

    <p>You know how it is to find a decent place in Lagos. As you've listed your apartment, there's a real chance that when you pack out, someone who genuinely needs it walks straight in — no agents, no runaround.</p>

    <hr class="divider">

    <div class="section-label">What we need from you</div>
    <p>To confirm the listing and get it in front of the right people, we need a few photos or a short video of the place. It doesn't have to be a production — a quick walkthrough, outdoor shots, even photos from before you moved in work fine.</p>

    <div class="step-row"><div class="dot"></div><div class="step-text">This helps us put a real visual on the apartment.</div></div>
    <div class="step-row"><div class="dot"></div><div class="step-text">Once we have it, we confirm the listing and connect a serious seeker directly.</div></div>
    <div class="step-row"><div class="dot"></div><div class="step-text">No one gets your contact until you're comfortable with the connection.</div></div>

    <div class="cta-wrap">
      <a href="https://wa.me/2348162373553?text=Hello%2C%20I%20just%20listed%20my%20place%20on%20RentPal%20and%20I%20want%20to%20share%20images." class="cta-btn">Send photos on WhatsApp →</a>
    </div>

    <hr class="divider">

    <div class="reward-box">
      <p>If the person taking over your place is open to it, there's sometimes room for a small arrangement between both parties — we'll facilitate that conversation where it's appropriate. We keep things fair on both sides.</p>
    </div>

    <hr class="divider">

    <div class="section-label" style="text-align:center;">Stay in the loop</div>
    <p style="text-align:center;">Join our Telegram channel — that's where we post confirmed listings and updates first.</p>
    <div class="tg-wrap">
      <a href="https://t.me/rentpal_lagos" class="tg-btn">Join t.me/rentpal_lagos →</a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      — The RentPal Team<br>
      <a href="https://rentpal.com">rentpal.com</a> · Lagos, Nigeria<br><br>
      You're receiving this because you listed an apartment at rentpal.com
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
